column3:
Map Tag - Enter your Map Fitler Tag here exactly as you’ve entered them when creating your map.
They must be exact in order to apply the correct filter/category. To apply multiple tags
to this location, separate by a comma.
column5: Link location to another page? Y/N
column12: Include on Selected Map(s) Location  List? Y/N
column14: Pin Image URL (Leave blank to use Map’s Default pin image)
column16:
Gallery Images: Enter the url of the images you’d like to include in the gallery,
separated by a comma.
